# Nginx Reverse Proxy for Laravel, FastAPI, MySQL, Redis

## Image
- `nginx:1.25` (or `nginx:1.27-alpine`)

## Features
- Gzip enabled
- HTTP/2 enabled
- SSL/TLS with Let's Encrypt support
- ACME challenge routing
- Security headers:
  - X-Frame-Options
  - X-Content-Type-Options
  - Strict-Transport-Security

## SSL Configuration (Production)

### HTTP Server (Port 80)
```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;
    server_name ${DOMAIN};

    # ACME challenge for Let's Encrypt
    location /.well-known/acme-challenge/ {
        root /var/www/letsencrypt;
    }

    # Redirect all other HTTP to HTTPS
    location / {
        return 301 https://$host$request_uri;
    }
}
```

### HTTPS Server (Port 443)
```nginx
server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    listen [::]:443 ssl http2;
    server_name ${DOMAIN};

    # SSL Certificates
    ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/${DOMAIN}/fullchain.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/${DOMAIN}/privkey.pem;

    # Security
    ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;
    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;
    ssl_ciphers HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;
    ssl_session_timeout 1d;
    ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:10m;

    # Diffie-Hellman
    ssl_dhparam /etc/ssl/certs/dhparam.pem;

    # OCSP stapling
    ssl_stapling on;
    ssl_stapling_verify on;

    # Root folder
    root /var/www/html;
    index index.php index.html;

    # Proxy to Laravel/FastAPI/Node API
    location /api/ {
        proxy_pass http://api:8000/;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto https;
    }

    # Serve static files
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }
}
```

## Directories
- `/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf`
- `/var/www/html` (Laravel public)
- `/var/www/letsencrypt` (ACME challenge root)
- `/etc/letsencrypt` (Let's Encrypt certificates)
- `/etc/ssl/certs/dhparam.pem` (Diffie-Hellman parameters)

## Laravel Configuration
- Root: `/var/www/html/public`
- Index: `index.php`
- Route all traffic to `/index.php`

## FastAPI Configuration
- Proxy requests to: `http://fastapi:8000`

## Docker Compose SSL Integration

### Required Volumes
```yaml
volumes:
  - ./nginx/conf:/etc/nginx/conf.d
  - letsencrypt:/etc/letsencrypt
  - dhparam:/etc/ssl/certs
  - ./html:/var/www/html
  - ./letsencrypt:/var/www/letsencrypt
```

### Certbot Service
```yaml
certbot:
  image: certbot/certbot
  volumes:
    - letsencrypt:/etc/letsencrypt
    - ./letsencrypt:/var/www/letsencrypt
  command: >
    certonly --webroot
    --webroot-path=/var/www/letsencrypt
    --email ${EMAIL}
    --agree-tos
    --no-eff-email
    -d ${DOMAIN}
```

